#: admin/prayer-field-content.php:201
msgid ""
"Jane from Senegal found herself pregnant as a teenager and so somehow gave "
"her self an abortion. A few years later, she was pregnant again. This time "
"she decided to keep the baby, but in order to avoid shaming the family, her "
"parents forced her to abort. She was 5 months along, and the baby was born "
"alive. Her mother showed her the baby, and then buried it alive. And Jane "
"lived in the grief and anger and bitterness that followed this event.\n"
"\n"
"On Thursday night she walked through forgiveness with the team teaching soul "
"care. It was HARD. There were tears, but Jesus brought beautiful freedom to "
"her life.\n"
"\n"
"Pray for spiritual seekers [in location] and all over the Muslim world to "
"find freedom in Jesus as they follow His example in receiving forgiveness "
"for their sins and extending forgiveness to those who have wronged them."
msgstr ""
"\"Jane\" de Senegal se encontró embarazada cuando era adolescente y, de "
"alguna manera, se practicó un aborto. Unos años más tarde, estaba embarazada "
"de nuevo. Esta vez decidió quedarse con el bebé, pero para evitar avergonzar "
"a la familia, sus padres la obligaron a abortar. Tenía 5 meses y el bebé "
"nació vivo. Su madre le mostró el bebé y luego lo enterró vivo. Y Jane vivió "
"en el dolor, la ira y la amargura que siguieron a este evento.\n"
"\n"
"El jueves por la noche caminó a través del perdón con el equipo de enseñanza "
"del cuidado del alma. Fue dificil. Hubo lágrimas, pero Jesús trajo una "
"hermosa libertad a su vida.\n"
"\n"
"Ore por los buscadores espirituales [in location] y en todo el mundo "
"musulmán para buscar y discutir la Biblia con amigos."

#: admin/prayer-field-content.php:206
msgid ""
"“Then my enemies will turn back in the day when I call. This I know, that "
"God is for me.” (Psalm 56:9 ESV).\n"
"\n"
"Father God, would you plant the seed of holy confidence in the hearts of "
"your followers [in location]. May they grow in the humble, eternal assurance "
"of your completed work of grace so that even in the darkest nights of "
"persecution, loneliness, and temptation they might join the saints across "
"generations in saying \"This I know, that God is for me.\" (Psalm 56:9).\n"
msgstr ""
"\"Cuando yo te pida ayuda, huirán mis enemigos. Una cosa sé: ¡Dios está de "
"mi parte!\" (Salmos 56:9 NVI)\n"
"\n"
"Padre Dios, planta la semilla de la santa confianza en los corazones de tus "
"seguidores [in location]. Que crezcan en la humilde y eterna seguridad de tu "
"obra completa de gracia para que, incluso en las noches más oscuras de "
"persecución, soledad y tentación, puedan unirse a los santos de todas las "
"generaciones al decir: \"Una cosa sé: ¡Dios está de mi parte!\" (Salmo "
"56:9).\n"

#: admin/prayer-field-content.php:211
msgid ""
"In our lifetime, wouldn't it be sad if we spent more time washing dishes or "
"swatting flies or mowing the yard or watching television than praying for "
"world missions? — Dave Davidson"
msgstr ""
"En nuestra vida, ¿no sería triste si pasáramos más tiempo lavando platos, "
"papando moscas, cortando el césped o mirando televisión que orando por el "
"mundo de las misiones? - Dave Davidson"

#: admin/prayer-field-content.php:215
msgid ""
"God, we love you! As your Church, help us do what it takes to let the people "
