"Si la Gran Comisión es verdad, nuestros planes no son demasiado grandes; son "
"demasiado pequeños. - Pat Morley"

#: admin/prayer-field-content.php:238
msgid ""
"God, we love you! As your Church, help us do what it takes to let the people "
