#: admin/prayer-field-content.php:335
msgid ""
"Tauqeer is a seeker who has been talking to a believer online about whether "
"Mohammad is the greatest prophet or not? The believer asked him, \"Should we "
"follow someone who is dead or someone who is alive?\" This confused Tauqeer "
"and made him question his beliefs. He is questioning if Jesus was more than "
"a prophet. Most Muslims believe Jesus is just a prophet who came to teach "
"people good things and performed a lot of miracles.\n"
"                \n"
"Pray Taqueer will come to know Jesus did more than perform miracles and will "
"open his heart to the Truth."
msgstr ""
"Tauqeer es un buscador que ha estado hablando con un creyente en línea sobre "
"si Mahoma es el mayor profeta o no. El creyente le preguntó: \"¿Debemos "
"seguir a alguien que está muerto oa alguien que está vivo?\" Esto confundió "
"a Tauqeer y le hizo cuestionar sus creencias. Está cuestionando si Jesús fue "
"más que un profeta. La mayoría de los musulmanes creen que Jesús es solo un "
"profeta que vino a enseñar cosas buenas a la gente y realizó muchos "
"milagros.\n"
"                \n"
"Ore para que Taqueer llegue a saber que Jesús hizo más que hacer milagros y "
"abra su corazón a la Verdad."

#: admin/prayer-field-content.php:338
msgid ""
"“he says: “It is too light a thing that you should be my servant to raise up "
"the tribes of Jacob and to bring back the preserved of Israel; I will make "
"you as a light for the nations, that my salvation may reach to the end of "
